race.description: Ecom Commodities Country Boosted Bm 58 Handicap
race.comment: REGAL PROBLEM (7) stalked the leading division then let down a little too well for his rivals first-up in a 1200m Scone maiden. Lightly raced filly who finds a modest BM58 here and looks a huge chance to go back-to-back. SPORTS PAGE (2) took over a long way for home then was found wanting in the dying stages last time out over this distance at Coonabarabran. Down in class and drawn to enjoy a softer run today. Looks the obvious threat. LAISVAS (8) gave away a big start on straightening but made significant ground to finish a close fifth recently over this distance at Moree. Mikayla Weir gets the best out of this mare and they reunite. Right in contention. AUTUMN SONG (3) has been safely held at his last three runs, all at 1600m. Worth another chance coming back in trip. STARLINK (1) is a three-time winner at this distance who has struggled lately in BM66 races. Can improve back in this grade.
